	('Jun was furious about it, but he kept his word','Jun đã rất tức giận nhưng anh ấy đã giữ lời hứa','00:14:22.950','00:14:25.410','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('And now my dad has three months to pay off his debt','Và bây giờ ba tôi có ba tháng để trả hết nợ','00:14:25.630','00:14:27.790','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('I\'m helping him out by teaching karate classes to earn money, something I really enjoy','Tôi đang giúp ba mình bằng cách dạy karate để kiếm tiền, điều tôi thực sự thích làm','00:14:28.050','00:14:31.830','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('Everything was great','Mọi thứ đều tuyệt vời','00:14:32.330','00:14:33.350','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('Too great','Quá tuyệt vời','00:14:33.650','00:14:34.190','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('Until..','Cho đến khi..','00:14:34.670','00:14:35.170','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('Yukiko, I gotta tell you something','Yukiko, tôi phải nói với cậu một chuyện','00:14:35.170','00:14:36.850','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('I..','Tôi..','00:14:37.190','00:14:37.670','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('I have to go abroad to study','Tôi phải đi du học','00:14:37.670','00:14:38.950','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('I\'ll leave tomorrow','Ngày mai tôi sẽ đi','00:14:39.250','00:14:40.490','your-animated-story-show-2'),
	('What?','Gì cơ?','00:14:40.850','00:14:41.330','your-animated-story-show-2'),
